<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n29040g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n29" href="#n29040g">N29 (VI.B.21)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n29all.htm#n29040g"> 40(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Melchior / Balthasar Kaspar </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The magi were priests of the Medes and Persians, a term applied to the wise men from the East who followed a star to Bethlehem, where they gave gifts to the Christ Child. A seventh-century tradition gives their names as Gaspar, Melchior and Balthasar, the first-named being a negro. </mm> </dd></dl>
